description: HealthCUBE is the first global decentralized & customized healthcare platform gathering healthcare data with smart healthcare IoT devices. In the global medical market environment, you can use IoT healthcare devices to check your family's health condition and receive heath analysis service via a healthcare platform based on artificial intelligence (AI) which we named "HealthCUBE". We aim to embody it as a customized healthcare platform service that provides the services needed for individuals' healthcare ranging from health checkup at home to health analysis using AI to telemedicine by healthcare professionals and to treatment at hospitals. The HealthCUBE token (HCC) is a utility token and fuels the HealthCUBE ecosystem. It can be used for rewards, payments or access to services within the platform.
name: HealthCUBE
